rs are plausible, that the two FRB classes have\ndifferent origins, or each has experienced distinctive phases or been subject\nto its own physical processes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Nov 2020 21:54:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 4 Nov 2020 03:33:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-05"}
