2)}$\nappears due to an increase in CF potential denoted by the parameter\n$A_2^0\\langle r^2\\rangle$ ($A_4^0\\langle r^4\\rangle$) caused by hybridization\nbetween 3$d$-electrons of Fe on 8$i$ (8$j$) site and 5$d$ and 6$p$ valence\nelectrons on Sm site. It is verified that the requirement for the appearance of\nFOMP is given as $-K_2<K_1<-6K_2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2020 03:17:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-02"}
