nce guarantees hold for the strongly anharmonic case of liquid\nwater. Both analytical and numerical results indicate that BCOCB excels over\nother known integrators in terms of accuracy, efficiency, and stability with\nrespect to time-step for practical applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2020 10:10:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 9 Nov 2020 18:52:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-11"}
