 the scientific literature. Smart-contracts source code\nhas been validated by EtherScan and each contract comes with its own associated\nsoftware metrics as computed by the freely available software PASO. Moreover,\nSmart Corpus can be easily extended, as the number of new smart-contracts\nincreases day by day.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2020 14:18:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-04"}
